Generally we define the optional field as '''yes''' to display them (for default off fields) and '''no''' to remove them (for default on fields).

The examples below show how to use the '''ratifier''', '''NR'''/'''nation''' and '''code1'''/'''legend1''' fields.

====Usage examples====
;Lists of records in swimming articles
World records:
<pre>
{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International Swimming Federation{{!}}FINA}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International Swimming Federation{{!}}FINA}}</blockquote>

Continental records:
<pre>
{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=Ligue Européenne de Natation{{!}}LEN|WR=yes}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=Ligue Européenne de Natation{{!}}LEN|WR=yes}}</blockquote>

National records:
<pre>
{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=British Swimming|WR=yes|ER=yes|CR=yes}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=British Swimming|WR=yes|ER=yes|CR=yes}}</blockquote>

Event/championships with no timetrials, no B-finals, and intermediate records not recognised:
<pre>
{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International University Sports Federation{{!}}FISU|WR=yes|†=no|tt=no|b=no}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International University Sports Federation{{!}}FISU|WR=yes|†=no|tt=no|b=no}}</blockquote>

Event/championships with no timetrials, no semifinals, no relays and intermediate records not recognised:
<pre>
{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=FINA|WR=yes|r=no|sf=no|tt=no|b=no}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=FINA|WR=yes|r=no|sf=no|tt=no|b=no}}</blockquote>

Event/championships with no timetrials, no semifinals, no B-final, and intermediate records not recognised:
<pre>
{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International Paralympic Committee{{!}}IPC|IPCWR=yes|tt=no|sf=no|b=no|†=no}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{Swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=International Paralympic Committee{{!}}IPC|IPCWR=yes|tt=no|sf=no|b=no|†=no}}</blockquote>

;Personal bests section of swimmer's biography article
<pre>
{{swimmingrecordlegend|WR=yes|ER=yes|nation=Swedish}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{swimmingrecordlegend|WR=yes|ER=yes|nation=Swedish}}</blockquote>

;World record progression article
<pre>
{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=FINA|yd=yes}}
</pre>
<blockquote>{{swimmingrecordlegend|ratifier=FINA|yd=yes}}</blockquote>

